{
  "name": "@huo15/openclaw-enhance",
  "version": "5.8.3",
  "description": "火一五·克劳德·龙虾增强插件 v5.8.2 — chore-only release：刷 ClawHub plugin tag（release.sh 之前默认只 --tags latest 没刷 plugin tag → plugin tag 卡在 5.7.9 那个 bare pluginApi=2026.2.24 老版本 → `openclaw plugins update` 报 'requires plugin API 2026.2.24, but runtime exposes 2026.4.29'）；同步修 release.sh 让以后默认 --tags latest,plugin。零代码逻辑改动。继承 v5.8.1 postinstall hint + v5.8.0 hook-profiler + v5.7.27 bot-share 持久化 + v5.7.26 session-bridge。",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "index.ts",
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": [
      "./index.ts"
    ],
    "build": {
      "openclawVersion": "2026.4.29"
    },
    "compat": {
      "pluginApi": ">=2026.4.24"
    }
  },
  "bin": {
    "openclaw-enhance-setup": "./scripts/setup.sh"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit",
    "release": "bash scripts/release.sh",
    "prepublishOnly": "npm run typecheck",
    "postinstall": "node scripts/postinstall.cjs"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "openclaw",
    "plugin",
    "enhance",
    "memory",
    "safety",
    "agent"
  ],
  "author": "jobzhao15",
  "license": "MIT",
  "peerDependencies": {
    "openclaw": "^2026.4.24"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@sinclair/typebox": "^0.34.49",
    "better-sqlite3": "^11.0.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/better-sqlite3": "^7.6.0",
    "typescript": "^5.5.0"
  },
  "files": [
    "index.ts",
    "openclaw.plugin.json",
    "src/**/*",
    "templates/**/*",
    "scripts/**/*"
  ],
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://cnb.cool/huo15/ai/huo15-openclaw-enhance"
  }
}
